OL,3,CCould eating peppermints help when you
OL,4,Chave a cold?
OL,6,FEating peppermints can increase
OL,7,Falertness in people who are ill with
OL,8,Fthe common cold, according to research.
OL,10,FScientists at Cardiff University
OL,11,Flooked at whether having a cold
OL,12,Fimpaired mood and performance, and if
OL,13,Fthese effects could be removed by
OL,14,Fsucking peppermints.
OL,16,FThey monitored 81 students over 10
OL,17,Fweeks and during that time 17
OL,18,Fparticipants developed a mild upper
OL,19,Frespiratory tract illness.
