OL,3,CCould eating peppermints help when you
OL,4,Chave a cold?
OL,6,FSix of the ill participants were given
OL,7,Fpeppermints, six were given
OL,8,Fbutterscotch, and five were not given
OL,9,Fsweets.
OL,11,FOf the 64 healthy controls, 21 sucked
OL,12,Fpeppermint, 22 were given placebo
OL,13,Fsweets, and 21 did not eat any sweets.
OL,15,FThe healthy controls and unwell
OL,16,Fparticipants were given tests for
OL,17,Ftheir mood, performance, and time
OL,18,Freaction tasks.
