OL,3,CCould eating peppermints help when you
OL,4,Chave a cold?
OL,6,FThe study confirmed that having a cold
OL,7,Fwas associated with slower reaction
OL,8,Ftimes, slower eye movements and
OL,9,Freduced alertness.
OL,11,FThey found that sucking a peppermint
OL,12,Fincreased alertness in both those with
OL,13,Fcolds and those who were healthy.
