OL,3,CCould eating peppermints help when you
OL,4,Chave a cold?
OL,6,FThey found that eating peppermints
OL,7,Finfluenced malaise because it soothed
OL,8,Fthe signals from the body to the brain.
OL,10,FDr Andy Smith, who led the research,
OL,11,Fsaid: "When people are sick with a
OL,12,Fmild upper respiratory tract illness,
OL,13,Fthey will likely experience malaise `
OL,14,Fa general discomfort and a lack of
OL,15,Fwell-being.
OL,17,F"This can impact performance and
OL,18,Freduce our alertness.
