OL,3,CCould eating peppermints help when you
OL,4,Chave a cold?
OL,6,F"Vapours are known to have therapeutic
OL,7,Fbenefits ` and aromatics, such as
OL,8,Fmint, have been shown in previous
OL,9,Fresearch to have an impact on our
OL,10,Fwellbeing when ill and in perfect
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,F"We thought it was plausible that
OL,14,Fpeppermints might help reduce the
OL,15,Fmalaise associated with the common
OL,16,Fcold and its symptoms.
OL,18,F"Our results confirmed that common
OL,19,Fcold illnesses are associated with
OL,20,Fslower psychomotor speed and reduced
OL,21,Falertness.
