OL,3,CCould eating peppermints help when you
OL,4,Chave a cold?
OL,6,F"But sucking on a peppermint, compared
OL,7,Fto a butterscotch or nothing, during a
OL,8,Fcold can increase your alertness.
OL,10,F"These results show that, with the
OL,11,Fright understanding, simple things can
OL,12,Fbe done to improve our wellbeing when
OL,13,Funwell ` and that includes eating a
OL,14,Fpeppermint to help with a cold."
